Name: Coin Pickers
About the game: Running across this maze-type of environment, you will have to open doors and avoid dangers to pass through the final door. Simple but cool. Classic but fresh at the same time. Its a One level game, made simple but mostly focused on texturing and modeling details. With easy and friendly controllers, this game is made to be fast but fun to play at the same time!
